Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Is there someone you want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Everyone has several people\Naround them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}whom they hate, or want to punch,\Nor want them to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Among those people,\Nthere must be at least one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}you would even want dead,\Nor to kill, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, it is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The document you prepared\Nwas inadequate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that's why the client is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why the pause?\NYou think it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't, but I wrote that\Naccording to what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Even so, correct it\Nif it's a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Our division doesn't need someone\Nwho takes no initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Our company doesn't need one,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}and society itself\Ndoesn't need one either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Forget it. You should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Quit your job and quit being a man!\NJust quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It feels much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}However, not many people can\Ngo so far in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why doesn't anyone do that, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Because our ethics\Ntell us it's not good to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Or is it the moral values?\NA sense of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Because our logical mind as a person\Nis functioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The biggest reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Because we don't want to\Nget arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Do you know what the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}between the murderers and\Nthe victims in this country is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Relationship between\Nmurderers and victims"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}about 90 percent of the victims\Nwere killed by someone they knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:01:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}if you were killed by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}there's a 90 percent chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that it was by a family member,\Nsomeone you were seeing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}a friend, or a colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You might be killed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}by the person sitting next to you,\Nwhom you're watching the telly with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That is why the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}checks out\Nthe victim's social network.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Society itself\Ndoesn't need one either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Forget it. You should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Quit your job and quit being a man!\NJust quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Just now, because I'm an outsider\Nand I have no motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}almost nobody would suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Let's say you want to kill person A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If you aren't related to A\Nin any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}even if you kill A,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}the chance of you being arrested\Nis nearly zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The above is only a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Who would've thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}some people actually\Ntry to carry out the theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It has been Naoto Takenaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Your Turn to Kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Chiunque Kuramae"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Episode 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Have you got that?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Let's lean it back, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- All right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Ready, go! Lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry, it's difficult to\Nfollow your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 302, Shota Tezuka"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- I'll lean it back.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay... Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Turn left.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Sorry, we're at the farthest back.\N- It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Please put it in front of\Nthe bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Where should I put it?\N- In the bedroom, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Over there. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Great. Is this the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 302, Nana Tezuka"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nana, we're moving the fridge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hang in there for a bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm so sorry!\NIt's okay. I'll fix it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yeah. Give me a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's so heavy!\NSorry, put it down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Thank you!\N- Handsome guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thanks for helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But we've only started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}My reward for\Ncompleting the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}There are children looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 104, Yoko Ishizaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 104, Kenji Ishizaki,\NFumiyo Ishizaki, Kazuo Ishizaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm glad we took the plunge\Nand bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You had to pay\Nthe whole sum of deposit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You said that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- It's our money, right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Should I buy us lunch at\Nthe convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- No, I'll go with you.\N- It's okay. Have a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Where is the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Go to the main road, turn right,\Nand there is one 100 metres ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 202, Sawa Kuroshima"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I forgot my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nana, sorry. Throw it down, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Hurry up!\N- Catch it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- I caught it!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, look out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, it's totally all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 502, Misato Akaike"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 502, Sachiko Akaike,\NGoro Akaike"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I wish we could grow old like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I haven't been\Ngetting enough sleep lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Like a child on the night\Nbefore going hiking,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}when I think about the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I get so excited that I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}In addition, my husband\Nwho is over 10 years younger than me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}happily has me\Ntwisted around his little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It appears that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am never going to get enough sleep\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am Tokoshima, the manager here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Manager, Hiroshi Tokoshima"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You didn't come to say hello,\Nso I came myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm checking the current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We have many issues
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}regarding returning tenants\Ntheir deposit when they move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me, we bought this flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Two gross stains on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Is this a bookshelf?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Use metal fittings\Nto prevent it from overturning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Mystery Series"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}May I close it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Newlyweds got themselves\Na semi-double bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We didn't rent the flat.\NIs this necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Whatever. Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I give everybody one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wow, he gave us this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It {\i1}seems{\i} that\Nthe manager made it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He made it himself?\NThat's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He said he gives one to everyone who\Nmoves in, and hung it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wow, isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wait... Isn't it rude\Nto take it off right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But the flat opposite\Ndoesn't hang it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But look... Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}This person uses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I wonder what our neighbour is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hello, I am Tezuka\Nand we've moved in next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh! Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am Ono, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 301, Mikiha Ono"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Please have this if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- See you.\N- See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Are you siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, we're a married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx232\fscy217}I see.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, our residents' association\Nwill have a meeting later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I will introduce you to\Nthe other residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Residents' association?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Only one person per household\Nhas to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's held once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's too trivial to be held\Nonce a month, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'll close my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm Tezuka and we've moved in\Nto the flat opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 304, Sora Kitagawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Hello.\N- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}This is just to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, I don't live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am Kojima,\Nand I live in Room 102.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 102, Kayo Kojima"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}See you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'll give it to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You're upstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We live opposite you,\Nso let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Should we have given a gift\Nto the lady on the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- It was a bit awkward.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We don't know\Nhow many people we should greet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Is this broken? It doesn't ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The flat there is unoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 501, Go Sano"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}My mind is exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No way! You can't be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Aren't you happy to\Nhave more friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm jealous of how tough you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Anyway, have you realised something,\NDetective Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Among the people we met, there was\Nsomething wrong with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But there's something wrong\Nwith all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Are we doing our usual thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Orangutan Time starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But I am tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Tell me, who was the weirdest\Namong the people we just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well... The last man we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yes. Why was he weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The flat there is unoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He was carrying a very large bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}His boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The flat there is unoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It was sunny outside,\Nbut he was wearing rain boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yes, I realised that too.\NWhy do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wait.\NThe residents' association meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We have to.\NFirst impression is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But we haven't unpacked our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Maybe I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Only one person needs to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Let's play rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Ready? Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We think alike,\Nso it always ends in a draw
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}when we play rock-paper-scissors\Nand it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}My husband works as\Na fitness trainer at a gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am a designer and I work at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wow, you are a designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 101, Yuzuru Kuzumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Do you participate in fashion shows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I design sports equipment, so I\Ndon't participate in shows often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Who is a designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 403, Atsushi Fujii"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, it's the lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am Tezuka, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}She said her husband works as\Na fitness trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Both you and your husband\Nhave a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 402, Sanae Enomoto"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The gentleman is your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I assumed\Nhe is your younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Your age gap is so huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am 15 years older.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}By the way, they have no children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I've verified that\Nthey have no pet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}People don't like the manager
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}checking their flat\Non the very first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But many married couples\Nthat have no children keep cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why do you have the prejudice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 304, Sumika Kitagawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}By the way,\Nit was 37,800,800 yen, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Your flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's been advertised many times,\Nso we all know. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Anyway, it has gotten a lot cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, an accident happened there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 201, Keisuke Ukita"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He is just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, Mr Ukita!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I was joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It gets older every year,\Nso the price becomes lower too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But I was surprised that\Nthe price got lower than 40 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It means that\Nthe money we have is getting less!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If there are so many bugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}what did you update it for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 404, Yuki Etou"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The meeting is going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I won't attend today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 103, Junichiro Tamiya"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What caused it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We won't start in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We should be here five minutes\Nearlier, but I'm two minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Chairlady, please start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}13 residents are present\Nand five are absent. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay, let's start this month's\Nresidents' association meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}So... Regarding the person in charge\Nthis year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}we haven't appointed the person\Nin charge of cleaning last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}would anyone volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But isn't it the manager's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Someone is against\Nthe raise of management fees!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's why in exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}you guys will clean\Nthe rubbish dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- The majority agreed last time!\N- Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Fine"? The majority agreed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Mr Tokoshima,\Nplease speak a bit more softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Mr Tamiya...\N- Mr Tokoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't know what the right amount\Nof management fee is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}so I won't judge anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But I think cleaning the place where\Nwe live, by ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}is a rudiment of day-to-day living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I think there are people\Nbusy working every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}but why don't we clean\Nthe rubbish dump ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What Tamiya said\Nwas a bit too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 203, Xinyi"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Xinyi, when you talk to\Nsomeone older,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}you'd better address them\Nmore politely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The way you apologise too...\NWell, let's forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's not too bad. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Detective novels"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Miss Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay, Miss Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Mrs Tezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Miss Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay, we've decided that\NRoom 401's Miss Kinoshita
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}will be in charge of cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Miss Kinoshita didn't come today.\NIs this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If she's got a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}complain to the seven people\Nwho voted for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I didn't vote for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That means either Mr Tamiya\Nor Mrs Tezuka did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I voted for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}She's fussy about\Nsorting rubbish to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Miss Kinoshita might be happy\Nto be in charge of cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, she might open our big bags\Nto check them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Right? You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}In other words, you'll just make\NMiss Kinoshita do the job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We've decided,\Nso let's stop our discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- See you, guys!\N- See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well then, let's have\Nour usual little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Mrs Tezuka.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The residents have a chat now,\Nas communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Do join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Don't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}People in charge of\Nmoney-collection and snacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- please help.\N- Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Ms Kitagawa, do stay behind\Noccasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Mrs Tezuka wants to talk to you too.\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Everyone,\NMrs Kitagawa will join too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Have you done that?\N- Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We collect money from all residents\Nfor snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}How much should I give?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You are free to give\Nthe amount you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}but if you give less than 1,000 yen,\Nsomeone will complain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Guys, you're staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Should I lend you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry, I will give you back later.\NWhat is your flat number?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Next meeting will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}This is the amount you gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Have some.\NWe don't want any leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm Room 502's Akaike,\Nand I'm in charge of the snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nice to meet you. I'm Tezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- You know...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I can remember something I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I have heard what your name is just\Nnow, you don't have to repeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Newcomer.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Do you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Wait a second!\N- You said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- What's the matter?\N- This guy said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that all the residents here hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He said you wanted to kill me\Nthree minutes after you met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It was only at first, but not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's why I asked the newcomer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You're so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}When we met just now,\Ndid you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why would she think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Because everyone has a moment\Nwhen they want to kill someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}or just want the person dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Usually people do! You do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}See? Nobody does!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But their reaction shows\Nthat they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}why don't we change the topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Mr Tamiya, I hate people\Nwho give fancy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm sure that everyone does!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If you mean I just want them gone\Nand isn't necessarily dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}then I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}They're the same thing.\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Hey, Fujii, you're the most likely\None to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.37,0:23:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't know why you said\NI'm the most likely,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}but I was bullied\Nwhen I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You want the bully dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Not just the bully,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I want all the people who pretended\Nthey saw nothing gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You're so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}When I was still working, I was\Nalways sexually harassed by my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.39,0:24:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I used to want that guy dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I wanted him to die once,\Ncome back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.08,0:24:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}then die once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why would he want to\Nsexually harass Mrs Akaike?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Saying that is\Nsexual harassment too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He was too nervous\Nto harass the pretty ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that's why he harassed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.36,0:24:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, I hate people who doesn't put\Ntheir wind chime away in autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The tinkle is so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.76,0:24:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}it makes you go crazy when it keeps\Ntinkling on a windy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But would you kill someone for\Nsomething like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.12,0:24:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I want to,\Nif I wouldn't be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.24,0:24:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But I would be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.95,0:24:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.91,0:24:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But the police first check\Namong the people the victim knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.96,0:24:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}whether someone has a motive\Nto kill the victim or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's why even if it's trivial,\Nif you have a motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.83,0:25:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}you'll end up being arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.39,0:25:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}My husband and I\Nlove mystery novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.39,0:25:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"The Murders in the Rue Morgue"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.79,0:25:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Detective Conan"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.39,0:25:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}So, on the contrary, they won't find\Nout if we have no motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.71,0:25:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Don't kill someone without a motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.35,0:25:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I mean, for example,\Nif I ask a killer to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.07,0:25:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}but the killer and you\Ndon't know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.04,0:25:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's difficult to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.68,0:25:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Where can you find a killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.63,0:25:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}And I think they're expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.59,0:25:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If you pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.19,0:25:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}How much can make you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.11,0:25:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.07,0:25:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- 10 million?\N- It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.31,0:25:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.79,0:25:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- What? You can pay 10 million?\N- I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.55,0:25:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's how rich you'd expect\Na doctor would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.76,0:25:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I can, but I won't pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.52,0:25:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.68,0:25:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You can kill\Nthe person I hate instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.16,0:25:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I will kill the person\Nyou want to kill, in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.56,0:25:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.17,0:25:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But keeping the secret would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.30,0:26:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yes!\NWhen knowing the victim and motive are removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.47,0:26:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}creating a situation where murders\Nare mutually exchanged
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.41,0:26:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}will make it more difficult for secrets to leak out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.55,0:26:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.03,0:26:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's murder-swap, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.37,0:26:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But the person I want to kill and I\Ndon't know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.15,0:26:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You can kill them yourself?\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.94,0:26:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Somehow our chat is\Ngetting frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It is just an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.66,0:26:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But now I'm curious about\Nwhat the person is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.51,0:26:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.39,0:26:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I can tell you, Mrs Tezuka,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.91,0:26:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}if you tell me\Nwhom you want to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.19,0:26:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Me?\N- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.83,0:26:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You don't seem to want to kill\Nanyone, that's why we asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.59,0:26:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You look like\Nyou wouldn't even kill a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.11,0:26:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, of course I kill bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.35,0:26:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You love killing bugs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.51,0:26:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.19,0:26:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Do you live on macarons?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.14,0:26:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.90,0:26:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, I want to ask who each one of\Nyou want to kill, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.71,0:27:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.19,0:27:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why don't we reveal it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.27,0:27:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No! What do we do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.55,0:27:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Frankly, you must be tired of\Nthe Werewolf game.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.10,0:27:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Indeed, I am executed by\Nthe villagers every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.54,0:27:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}See? It's villager again!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.02,0:27:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}So, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}we can write names on\Nballot papers like just now
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.22,0:27:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}and show everyone without letting\Nanyone know who wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.26,0:27:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why do you have to go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.46,0:27:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't want to show everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.58,0:27:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I will, if I'll show\Nonly one person in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.30,0:27:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}All right, then.\NWhy don't we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.75,0:27:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, it's the box we just used.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.15,0:27:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We'll write whom we want to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.23,0:27:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If I don't participate,\Nmaybe they'll talk behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.71,0:27:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The other people besides me\Nseem to be bothered by that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.43,0:27:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Don't look at other people's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.57,0:27:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.69,0:28:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.30,0:28:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.45,0:28:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.65,0:28:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Please write the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.09,0:28:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.23,0:28:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I think we'd better not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.15,0:28:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}This is just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.79,0:28:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Or is there someone\Nthat you really want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.34,0:28:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Excuse me.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.78,0:28:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}May I borrow a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.94,0:28:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.14,0:28:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- There you go.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.36,0:29:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Everyone, put the piece of paper\Nin the tin after you've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.95,0:30:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay, as we said just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.79,0:30:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}we'll do it like exchanging gifts\Nat the Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.87,0:30:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Okay.\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.51,0:30:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.00,0:30:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's said that\Nwhat is left behind brings you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.56,0:30:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.72,0:30:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Do not show other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.36,0:30:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.12,0:30:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.00,0:30:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Although it's a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.72,0:31:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}it's the first time I see\Nwords written...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.92,0:31:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}when someone was thinking about\Nwanting to kill another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.79,0:31:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.83,0:31:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Takafumi Kono"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.64,0:31:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that this person has no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.72,0:31:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that someone wants to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.57,0:31:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.61,0:31:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am home!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.01,0:31:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wow, you've tidied it up! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.73,0:31:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay. How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.93,0:31:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.21,0:31:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.41,0:31:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Thanks for attending it.\N- Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.85,0:31:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.65,0:31:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}will we submit this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.01,0:31:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Marriage registration form"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.49,0:31:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Yeah.\N- Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.85,0:31:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Your reply is not serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.97,0:31:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.89,0:31:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You said you wanted to submit it\Nafter we move here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:32:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Does our age gap still bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.60,0:32:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Having a 15 year age gap\Nis quite common.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Quite common is exaggerating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.84,0:32:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I want to tell everyone properly\Nthat we are married too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.44,0:32:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You see, I feel a bit like I'm lying\Nto our neighbours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.14,0:32:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am a bit scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.14,0:32:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.74,0:32:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I feel that you are\Nvery close to me, Shota,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.90,0:32:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I feel that you've gotten a lot\Ncloser to me than when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.94,0:32:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But our age gap can never be filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}There will be a 15 year gap\Nbetween us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.26,0:32:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The fact that\Nwe can never fill it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}makes me scared somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.54,0:32:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, why are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.98,0:32:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.98,0:32:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Maybe I am not scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.98,0:32:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I just feel a little lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}In the coming 15 years in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.53,0:33:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}you will grow up and\Nyour sense of values will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.92,0:33:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}When you are about as old\Nas I am now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.40,0:33:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}will you still love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.72,0:33:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I have the same worries too,\Nbecause you're also going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am too old to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.78,0:33:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.95,0:33:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sorry for bringing this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.75,0:33:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Look at the setting sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.83,0:33:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.83,0:33:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Come on, let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.74,0:33:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Marriage registration form\NShota Tezuka, Nana Hibino"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.42,0:33:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm glad that we bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.55,0:33:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You said it the second time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.38,0:34:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}About what we were saying\Njust now...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.67,0:34:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I want to grow to become\Na more reliable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.34,0:34:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}So I'm going to grow\Nand I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.46,0:34:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}And I think you are still going to\Ngrow and change too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But even if we both change
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.85,0:34:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}and become someone\Ndifferent from who we are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.93,0:34:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I will still fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.01,0:34:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.97,0:34:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}We'll change many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.07,0:34:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}we'll like each other\Nafter we have changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.91,0:34:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}and we will fall in love\Nwith each other again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.87,0:34:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}So don't get worried and let's go to\Nregister our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.10,0:34:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.36,0:34:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.82,0:35:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What will we have for supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.22,0:35:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'll make something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.31,0:35:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's right.\NWe have to buy some groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.58,0:35:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's okay, you went to buy lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.86,0:35:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Keep training\Nyour internal oblique muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.46,0:35:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh? You remember it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.38,0:35:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Wait, where is my coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.10,0:35:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Your coat is probably there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.47,0:35:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- There?\N- No... Wait. Is it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.59,0:35:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Did I put it there?\N- No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.39,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.99,0:36:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.35,0:36:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- The manager said that, right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.91,0:36:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But I'm not bothered by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.83,0:36:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.75,0:36:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He also said that to me\Nwhen I first moved here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.91,0:36:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}that many childless couples\Nkeep cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, it's only me and my husband too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.11,0:36:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.30,0:36:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, I think the manager\Ndoesn't think before he speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.31,0:36:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's why I thought I shouldn't let\Neverything he says hurt my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.06,0:37:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Every time someone says\Nsomething awful to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.90,0:37:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I say something nice\Nto somebody twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.39,0:37:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am practising this,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.87,0:37:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}so that I can make\Nthe kindness in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.15,0:37:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Well, increase little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.98,0:37:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Is this weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.62,0:37:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No, I think your idea is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.87,0:37:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.63,0:37:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Go straight ahead\Nand you'll see a supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.47,0:37:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Turn left at the second corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.59,0:37:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Yes!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.11,0:37:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You can ask me anything\Nif you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.67,0:37:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I am the chairlady, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.03,0:37:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.31,0:37:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}By the way, what is your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.75,0:37:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.79,0:37:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nana, right?\NYou can call me Sanae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.87,0:37:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Oh, let me call you Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.11,0:37:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Let's be good friends, then.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.15,0:37:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- See you.\N- See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.05,0:38:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Chiunque Kuramae"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.25,0:38:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Person in charge of cleaning:\NRoom 401, Kinoshita. Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.81,0:38:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 401, Akane Kinoshita"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.96,0:39:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.36,0:39:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I didn't attend the residents'\Nassociation meeting this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.36,0:39:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 204, Jun Nishimura"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.77,0:39:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.64,0:40:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Where's your mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.88,0:40:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Working as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.08,0:40:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But I saw her just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.72,0:40:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}She went to work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.25,0:40:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.37,0:40:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's dark now, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.09,0:40:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.37,0:40:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}“Room 201 , Ryo Kakinuma, Airi Seno"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.28,0:40:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 203, Cuong"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.96,0:40:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 203, Iqbal"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.28,0:40:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's right... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.20,0:40:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}That's right.\NThen the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.80,0:41:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.36,0:41:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The opposite! Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.27,0:41:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Room 402, Masashi Enomoto"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.83,0:41:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Opposite? Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.62,0:41:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Right or left? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.70,0:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- The opposite.\N- The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.50,0:41:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Watch out! Look backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.31,0:41:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What? Opposite...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Thanks for supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.67,0:41:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- It was delicious.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.49,0:41:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But did you eat enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.19,0:41:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You don't have to force yourself\Nto limit your sugar intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.63,0:41:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm not forcing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.11,0:41:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- Really?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.27,0:41:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I'm a fitness trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.95,0:41:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}so I keep myself fit to\Ngain my clients' trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.31,0:41:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}And I just want to lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.99,0:41:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.83,0:41:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}You'll get fat\Nif you sleep right after you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.13,0:41:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.87,0:41:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.71,0:41:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What keys are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.75,0:42:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What? They aren't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.87,0:42:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Maybe it's the manager's?\NHe came inside this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.71,0:42:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}- I'll go and return them, then.\N- Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.67,0:42:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Yeah. I didn't see him,\Nso I'll go and say hello too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.51,0:42:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Manager's office"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.59,0:42:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.47,0:42:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Manager's office"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.19,0:43:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Excuse me, I am Room 302's Tezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.83,0:43:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.27,0:43:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He wasn't there. Maybe he has left?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.91,0:43:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I found his contact details.\NMaybe we can give it back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.15,0:43:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But wouldn't he be\Nworrying about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.47,0:43:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Are they the keys of his office?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.19,0:43:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}The door was open, I wanted to\Nlock it, but none of them fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.67,0:43:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Maybe they're his home's keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.27,0:43:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}But this looks like a car\Nor a motorcycle key.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.99,0:43:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Anyway, let's call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.15,0:43:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Nana, should you speak first?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.27,0:43:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.31,0:43:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I don't really know\Nhow to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.23,0:43:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.59,0:43:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I can't really explain it,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.51,0:43:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}but the other residents\Nhave trouble dealing with him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.03,0:43:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}To be honest, everyone hates him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.95,0:44:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He doesn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.07,0:44:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.47,0:44:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}What? He left his mobile here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.39,0:44:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.15,0:44:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}It's outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.31,0:44:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I can't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.23,0:45:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Our property manager"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.18,0:45:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Our property manager"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.18,0:45:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"Your Turn to Kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.67,0:45:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}Was he murdered by one of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.19,0:45:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}None of us wrote the manager, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.99,0:46:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}If someone killed for you, you have\Nto kill for someone. It's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.18,0:46:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}I know the answer.\NThe real culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.62,0:46:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx232\fscy217}"The drama is fiction"
